  15:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** \brief Implementation
  16:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** This file contains an example how to use the FoE services
  17:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** 
  18:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** \version 5.12
  19:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** 
  20:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** <br>Changes to version V5.11:<br>
  21:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** V5.12 FOE1: update new interface,move the FoE sample to sampleappl,add FoE application callback fun
  22:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** <br>Changes to version V5.10:<br>
  23:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** V5.11 FOE2: FoE_Read() check File name buffer before store the requested file name, add string term
  24:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** V5.11 TEST5: send a FoE busy on a FoE read request<br>
  25:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** V5.11 TEST9: "add behaviour 0x2020.7 (SDO requests on 0x3006.0 are set to pending until an FoE read
  26:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** <br>Changes to version V5.0:<br>
  27:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** V5.10 FOE2: Update file handling to support File sizes greater than 0x8000 Bytes (change value of "
  28:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** <br>Changes to version V4.20:<br>
  29:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** V5.0 FOE3: Add additional file name copy operation to provide name byte swapping<br>
  30:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** V5.0 FOE5: Add FoE test operation (FOE_SAVE_FILES need to be disabled). On download only the files 
  31:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** V5.0 FOE6: Save file if MBX 16Bit access is enabled<br>
  32:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** <br>Changes to version V4.11:<br>
  33:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** V4.20 FOE 2: Add File store compiler switch<br>
  34:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** V4.20 FOE 1: Removed FILESUPPORT<br>
  35:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** V4.11 FOE 1: nFileWriteOffset is now a 32bit variable to extend the maximum file size<br>
  36:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** <br>Changes to version V3.20:<br>
  37:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** V4.10 FOE 1-14: Filetransfer over FoE: Files can be read and stored to harddisk<br>
  38:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c ****                       without any filesizelimitation (FILESUPPORT must defined)
  39:../SSC/Src/foeappl.c **** */
